import React from "react";

function Header(){
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1" />

<title>
    CMU Face Mask Detector Admin
</title>


<link rel="stylesheet" href={process.env.PUBLIC_URL + "/stylesheets/bootstrap.css"} />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/app.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/plugins.css" />

<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/images/favicons/apple-touch-icon.png" />
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="/images/favicons/android-chrome-192x192.png" />
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="/images/favicons/android-chrome-256x256.png" />
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/images/favicons/favicon-32x32.png" />
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/images/favicons/favicon-16x16.png" />
<link rel="mask-icon" href="/images/favicons/safari-pinned-tab.svg" color="#f85d4c" />

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.amcharts.com/lib/3/plugins/export/export.css" type="text/css" media="all" />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff" />

<link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS" href="atom.xml" />

<script>
    var ASSET_PATH_BASE = '';
</script>

        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default Header;
